Package ca.on.oicr.gsi.shesmu.plugin.input

Annotation Interface ShesmuInputSource

@Retention(RUNTIME) @Target(METHOD) public @interface ShesmuInputSource
Indicate this method returns input for a particular format

The input format must be separately defined by InputFormat

This annotation should be applied to instance methods in PluginFile or static methods PluginFileType that return a Stream of input value and take no arguments. The generic type of the string must match with an existing input format.
